{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-tsx","path":"/what-is-prometheus/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/deada13263aaf9b4e16dc560fd0ccebb/6edca/1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 60.13513513513513%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Prometheus아키텍처\"\n        title=\"Prometheus아키텍처\"\n        src=\"/static/deada13263aaf9b4e16dc560fd0ccebb/fcda8/1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/deada13263aaf9b4e16dc560fd0ccebb/12f09/1.png 148w,\n/static/deada13263aaf9b4e16dc560fd0ccebb/e4a3f/1.png 295w,\n/static/deada13263aaf9b4e16dc560fd0ccebb/fcda8/1.png 590w,\n/static/deada13263aaf9b4e16dc560fd0ccebb/efc66/1.png 885w,\n/static/deada13263aaf9b4e16dc560fd0ccebb/c83ae/1.png 1180w,\n/static/deada13263aaf9b4e16dc560fd0ccebb/6edca/1.png 1351w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><em>Prometheus는 메트릭 수집, 알림, 서비스 디스커버리 기능을 제공하는 오픈소스 모니터링 시스템입니다.</em></p>\n<p>Prometheus는 단기 작업을 위해 직접 스크랩 하거나\nshort-lived jobs를 push gateway를 통해 스크랩합니다.\n스크랩한 모든 sample(TSD, 시계열 데이터)을 local 저장소에 저장하고 이 데이터에 대한 규칙(rules)을 실행하여 기존 데이터에서 새 시계열을 집계 및 기록하거나 alert를 생성합니다.\nGrafana 또는 기타 APIConsumers를 사용해 수집된 데이터를 시각화할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"prometheus-특징\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#prometheus-%ED%8A%B9%EC%A7%95\" aria-label=\"prometheus 특징 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Prometheus 특징</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>TSD를 스크랩하고 저장하는 메인 Prometheus 서버</li>\n<li>Application 코드를 계측하기 위한 <a href=\"https://prometheus.io/docs/instrumenting/clientlibs/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Client Libraries</a></li>\n<li>short-lived jobs를 위한 push gateway</li>\n<li>특수 목적의 exportes (HAProxy, StatsD, Graphite)</li>\n<li>alert를 핸들링하는 (처리하는) alertManager</li>\n<li>다양한 지원 도구</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"prometheus-데이터-수집-방식\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#prometheus-%EB%8D%B0%EC%9D%B4%ED%84%B0-%EC%88%98%EC%A7%91-%EB%B0%A9%EC%8B%9D\" aria-label=\"prometheus 데이터 수집 방식 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Prometheus 데이터 수집 방식</h2>\n<p>Prometheus의 데이터 수집방식은 Pull 방식입니다. (Push 방식도 지원함)\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d06fff49c204ba4cf080295a662562a7/e8950/2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 23.64864864864865%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Push/Pull방식\"\n        title=\"Push/Pull방식\"\n        src=\"/static/d06fff49c204ba4cf080295a662562a7/fcda8/2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d06fff49c204ba4cf080295a662562a7/12f09/2.png 148w,\n/static/d06fff49c204ba4cf080295a662562a7/e4a3f/2.png 295w,\n/static/d06fff49c204ba4cf080295a662562a7/fcda8/2.png 590w,\n/static/d06fff49c204ba4cf080295a662562a7/efc66/2.png 885w,\n/static/d06fff49c204ba4cf080295a662562a7/c83ae/2.png 1180w,\n/static/d06fff49c204ba4cf080295a662562a7/e8950/2.png 2000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Push 방식 - 데이터를 가진 곳에서 필요한 곳(모니터링 서비스)으로 보내준다.</li>\n<li>Pull 방식 - 데이터가 필요한 곳(모니터링 서비스)에서 가진 곳에 접속해 데이터를 긁어간다(Scrape)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>이러한 방식들의 장단점은 4가지 측면에서 자세히 살펴 볼 수 있습니다.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>수집 대상이 Auto-scaling 등으로 가변적일 경우</li>\n<li>수집 대상의 데이터 유연성 측면</li>\n<li>보안 측면</li>\n<li>HA* 측면</li>\n</ol>\n<p>*프로그램 등의 시스템이 상당히 오랜 기간동안 지속적으로 정상 운영이 가능한 성질</p>\n<h3 id=\"1-수집대상이-가변적일-경우\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-%EC%88%98%EC%A7%91%EB%8C%80%EC%83%81%EC%9D%B4-%EA%B0%80%EB%B3%80%EC%A0%81%EC%9D%BC-%EA%B2%BD%EC%9A%B0\" aria-label=\"1 수집대상이 가변적일 경우 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. 수집대상이 가변적일 경우</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1da97a71775632b6f0a7af41d1157f47/efb68/3.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 35.13513513513513%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"가변적\"\n        title=\"가변적\"\n        src=\"/static/1da97a71775632b6f0a7af41d1157f47/fcda8/3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1da97a71775632b6f0a7af41d1157f47/12f09/3.png 148w,\n/static/1da97a71775632b6f0a7af41d1157f47/e4a3f/3.png 295w,\n/static/1da97a71775632b6f0a7af41d1157f47/fcda8/3.png 590w,\n/static/1da97a71775632b6f0a7af41d1157f47/efc66/3.png 885w,\n/static/1da97a71775632b6f0a7af41d1157f47/c83ae/3.png 1180w,\n/static/1da97a71775632b6f0a7af41d1157f47/efb68/3.png 2032w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\nPush 방식이 유리합니다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"2-수집-대상의-데이터-유연성-측면\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-%EC%88%98%EC%A7%91-%EB%8C%80%EC%83%81%EC%9D%98-%EB%8D%B0%EC%9D%B4%ED%84%B0-%EC%9C%A0%EC%97%B0%EC%84%B1-%EC%B8%A1%EB%A9%B4\" aria-label=\"2 수집 대상의 데이터 유연성 측면 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. 수집 대상의 데이터 유연성 측면</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8a64750e2f017deb3e18355d40d824d7/08485/4.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 29.72972972972973%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"유연성\"\n        title=\"유연성\"\n        src=\"/static/8a64750e2f017deb3e18355d40d824d7/fcda8/4.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8a64750e2f017deb3e18355d40d824d7/12f09/4.png 148w,\n/static/8a64750e2f017deb3e18355d40d824d7/e4a3f/4.png 295w,\n/static/8a64750e2f017deb3e18355d40d824d7/fcda8/4.png 590w,\n/static/8a64750e2f017deb3e18355d40d824d7/efc66/4.png 885w,\n/static/8a64750e2f017deb3e18355d40d824d7/c83ae/4.png 1180w,\n/static/8a64750e2f017deb3e18355d40d824d7/08485/4.png 2014w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\nPull 방식이 유리합니다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"3-보안-측면\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-%EB%B3%B4%EC%95%88-%EC%B8%A1%EB%A9%B4\" aria-label=\"3 보안 측면 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. 보안 측면</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/0a7b6060dfb09ec4b285729b2d6cfa0e/ed8a2/5.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 29.054054054054056%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"보안\"\n        title=\"보안\"\n        src=\"/static/0a7b6060dfb09ec4b285729b2d6cfa0e/fcda8/5.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/0a7b6060dfb09ec4b285729b2d6cfa0e/12f09/5.png 148w,\n/static/0a7b6060dfb09ec4b285729b2d6cfa0e/e4a3f/5.png 295w,\n/static/0a7b6060dfb09ec4b285729b2d6cfa0e/fcda8/5.png 590w,\n/static/0a7b6060dfb09ec4b285729b2d6cfa0e/efc66/5.png 885w,\n/static/0a7b6060dfb09ec4b285729b2d6cfa0e/c83ae/5.png 1180w,\n/static/0a7b6060dfb09ec4b285729b2d6cfa0e/ed8a2/5.png 1972w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\nPush 방식이 유리합니다. </p>\n<p>그 이유는 Pull 방식은 수집 대상에서 중앙 모니터링이 접근할 수 있는 IP, Port 등을 수신 대기해야합니다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"4-ha-측면\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#4-ha-%EC%B8%A1%EB%A9%B4\" aria-label=\"4 ha 측면 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>4. HA 측면</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d3516168bc6d34495f9d436dfd627df7/a4f52/6.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 29.72972972972973%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"HA\"\n        title=\"HA\"\n        src=\"/static/d3516168bc6d34495f9d436dfd627df7/fcda8/6.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d3516168bc6d34495f9d436dfd627df7/12f09/6.png 148w,\n/static/d3516168bc6d34495f9d436dfd627df7/e4a3f/6.png 295w,\n/static/d3516168bc6d34495f9d436dfd627df7/fcda8/6.png 590w,\n/static/d3516168bc6d34495f9d436dfd627df7/efc66/6.png 885w,\n/static/d3516168bc6d34495f9d436dfd627df7/c83ae/6.png 1180w,\n/static/d3516168bc6d34495f9d436dfd627df7/a4f52/6.png 2024w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\nPull 방식이 유리합니다.</p>\n<p>Push 방식은 수집 대상이 중앙에 데이터 전송을 재시도를 지속적으로 해야하므로 영향이 생깁니다.\nPull 방식은 중앙 모니터링이 장애가 발생하더라도 수집 대상에는 영향이 없습니다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"prometheus-metrics\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#prometheus-metrics\" aria-label=\"prometheus metrics permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Prometheus Metrics</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Metrics 구성\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/2928ab6a07b40e1a50c34206ae864cdc/d53ff/7.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 63.51351351351351%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"metrics\"\n        title=\"metrics\"\n        src=\"/static/2928ab6a07b40e1a50c34206ae864cdc/fcda8/7.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/2928ab6a07b40e1a50c34206ae864cdc/12f09/7.png 148w,\n/static/2928ab6a07b40e1a50c34206ae864cdc/e4a3f/7.png 295w,\n/static/2928ab6a07b40e1a50c34206ae864cdc/fcda8/7.png 590w,\n/static/2928ab6a07b40e1a50c34206ae864cdc/efc66/7.png 885w,\n/static/2928ab6a07b40e1a50c34206ae864cdc/d53ff/7.png 1068w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\nPrometheus 메트릭 구성은 아래와 같습니다.\n<code class=\"language-text\">메트릭이름{필드1=값,필드2=값} @시간 샘플데이터(float 64)</code></li>\n<li>Metrics 표현 형식\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f8b6a1a1a4e2ac0dce8882501b45e2d9/09ede/8.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 32.43243243243243%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"metrics\"\n        title=\"metrics\"\n        src=\"/static/f8b6a1a1a4e2ac0dce8882501b45e2d9/fcda8/8.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f8b6a1a1a4e2ac0dce8882501b45e2d9/12f09/8.png 148w,\n/static/f8b6a1a1a4e2ac0dce8882501b45e2d9/e4a3f/8.png 295w,\n/static/f8b6a1a1a4e2ac0dce8882501b45e2d9/fcda8/8.png 590w,\n/static/f8b6a1a1a4e2ac0dce8882501b45e2d9/efc66/8.png 885w,\n/static/f8b6a1a1a4e2ac0dce8882501b45e2d9/c83ae/8.png 1180w,\n/static/f8b6a1a1a4e2ac0dce8882501b45e2d9/09ede/8.png 1710w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\nPrometheus Metrics은 사람이 쉽게 이해할만한 표현 형식입니다.</li>\n<li># HELP 는 메트릭 이름, 간단한 설명(주석)</li>\n<li># TYPE 은 메트릭 타입 (Prometheus Metric Type : Counter, Gauge, Histogram, Summary)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"prometheus-아키텍처\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#prometheus-%EC%95%84%ED%82%A4%ED%85%8D%EC%B2%98\" aria-label=\"prometheus 아키텍처 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Prometheus 아키텍처</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/90c21ae2c2c41a1adf326fc5fc39a627/536c7/9.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 64.86486486486486%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"아키텍처\"\n        title=\"아키텍처\"\n        src=\"/static/90c21ae2c2c41a1adf326fc5fc39a627/fcda8/9.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/90c21ae2c2c41a1adf326fc5fc39a627/12f09/9.png 148w,\n/static/90c21ae2c2c41a1adf326fc5fc39a627/e4a3f/9.png 295w,\n/static/90c21ae2c2c41a1adf326fc5fc39a627/fcda8/9.png 590w,\n/static/90c21ae2c2c41a1adf326fc5fc39a627/efc66/9.png 885w,\n/static/90c21ae2c2c41a1adf326fc5fc39a627/c83ae/9.png 1180w,\n/static/90c21ae2c2c41a1adf326fc5fc39a627/536c7/9.png 1480w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n모니터링의 기능으로 아키텍처를 파악하면 3가지로 구분될 수 있습니다.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>수집 - 수집 대상으로 부터 Exporter를 설치, Prometheus Server가 Pull 방식으로 데이터 수집\nService Discover를 통해 Target 서버에 대한 정보를 편리하게 가져옴</li>\n<li>저장 - Prometheus는 Sample(시계열 데이터) 수집시, In-Memory에 저장하고 있다가 주기적으로 Disk에 Flush함</li>\n<li>서빙 - PromQL를 통해 질의하거나 외부 API 나 Prometheus Web UI, Grafana를 통해 데이터를 내보내거나 시각화</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"prometheus-적합성\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#prometheus-%EC%A0%81%ED%95%A9%EC%84%B1\" aria-label=\"prometheus 적합성 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Prometheus 적합성</h2>\n<h3 id=\"prometheus는-언제-적합한가\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#prometheus%EB%8A%94-%EC%96%B8%EC%A0%9C-%EC%A0%81%ED%95%A9%ED%95%9C%EA%B0%80\" aria-label=\"prometheus는 언제 적합한가 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Prometheus는 언제 적합한가?</h3>\n<p>이러한 경우에 Prometheus가 적합할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>단순 숫자로 된 시계열 기록</li>\n<li>모니터링과 고도의 동적인 서비스 지향 아키텍처 모니터링</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Prometheus는 MSA(Micro Service Architecture)에서 다차원 데이터 수집 및 쿼리 지원은 강점\nPrometheus는 모니터링 시스템으로서 안정성을 위해 설계되었고 각 프로메테우스 서버는 독립형이며 네트워크 스토리지 또는 원격 서비스에 의존하지 않습니다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"prometheus는-언제-적합하지-않는가\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#prometheus%EB%8A%94-%EC%96%B8%EC%A0%9C-%EC%A0%81%ED%95%A9%ED%95%98%EC%A7%80-%EC%95%8A%EB%8A%94%EA%B0%80\" aria-label=\"prometheus는 언제 적합하지 않는가 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Prometheus는 언제 적합하지 않는가?</h3>\n<p>요청당 청구 (per-request billing)과 같이 100% 정확도가 필요한 경우 수집된 데이터가 충분히 자세하고 완전하지 않을 수 있어서 좋은 선택이 아닐 수 있습니다.</p>\n<p>청구(billing)을 위해 데이터를 수집하고 분석하는데 다른 시스템을 사용하고 나머지 모니터링을 Prometheus를 사용하는게 가장 좋음</p>","excerpt":"Prometheus는 메트릭 수집, 알림, 서비스 디스커버리 기능을 제공하는 오픈소스 모니터링 시스템입니다. Prometheus는 단기 작업을 위해 직접 스크랩 하거나\nshort-lived jobs를 push gateway를 통해 스크랩합니다.\n스크…","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/what-is-prometheus/#prometheus-%ED%8A%B9%EC%A7%95\">Prometheus 특징</a></li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/what-is-prometheus/#prometheus-%EB%8D%B0%EC%9D%B4%ED%84%B0-%EC%88%98%EC%A7%91-%EB%B0%A9%EC%8B%9D\">Prometheus 데이터 수집 방식</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/what-is-prometheus/#1-%EC%88%98%EC%A7%91%EB%8C%80%EC%83%81%EC%9D%B4-%EA%B0%80%EB%B3%80%EC%A0%81%EC%9D%BC-%EA%B2%BD%EC%9A%B0\">1. 수집대상이 가변적일 경우</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/what-is-prometheus/#2-%EC%88%98%EC%A7%91-%EB%8C%80%EC%83%81%EC%9D%98-%EB%8D%B0%EC%9D%B4%ED%84%B0-%EC%9C%A0%EC%97%B0%EC%84%B1-%EC%B8%A1%EB%A9%B4\">2. 수집 대상의 데이터 유연성 측면</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/what-is-prometheus/#3-%EB%B3%B4%EC%95%88-%EC%B8%A1%EB%A9%B4\">3. 보안 측면</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/what-is-prometheus/#4-ha-%EC%B8%A1%EB%A9%B4\">4. HA 측면</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"/what-is-prometheus/#prometheus-metrics\">Prometheus Metrics</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/what-is-prometheus/#prometheus-%EC%95%84%ED%82%A4%ED%85%8D%EC%B2%98\">Prometheus 아키텍처</a></li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/what-is-prometheus/#prometheus-%EC%A0%81%ED%95%A9%EC%84%B1\">Prometheus 적합성</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/what-is-prometheus/#prometheus%EB%8A%94-%EC%96%B8%EC%A0%9C-%EC%A0%81%ED%95%A9%ED%95%9C%EA%B0%80\">Prometheus는 언제 적합한가?</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/what-is-prometheus/#prometheus%EB%8A%94-%EC%96%B8%EC%A0%9C-%EC%A0%81%ED%95%A9%ED%95%98%EC%A7%80-%EC%95%8A%EB%8A%94%EA%B0%80\">Prometheus는 언제 적합하지 않는가?</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","fields":{"slug":"/what-is-prometheus/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Prometheus란 무엇인가","date":"Feb 09, 2023","tags":["Prometheus","Monitoring"],"keywords":["Prometheus","Kubernetes"],"update":"Jan 01, 0001"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/what-is-prometheus/","series":[],"lastmod":"2023-02-09"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2027115977","694178885"]}